    <h1>
        ADD -> user roles:<br>
        <ul>
            <li>Add user roles: client_admin & client</li>
            <li>Client_admin: full access</li>
            <li>client: limited access</li>
            <li>Add Private/Public message (availalbe only for client_admin to choose)</li>
        </ul>
    </h1>
    <h1>
        ADD -> upload documents:<br>
        <ul>
        <li>Customer can't upload documents on their own, the request has to come from Bookkeeper</li>
        <li>Customer authorization: customer CAN see the requests for documents; CAN update existing request with the file that has been requested</li>
        <li>Customer CAN'T: create new upload document form; delete any requests;</li>
        <li>Bookkeeper authorization: CAN create new document request; CAN delete requests, CAN update requests;</li>
        </ul>
    </h1>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 tex-center">
            <h1>New Message</h1>        
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row well">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
            <%= render 'form' %>
            <%= link_to 'Back', messages_path %>
        </div>
    
</div>